replies.body:
I guess? Maybe people are assuming that I'm complaining about all the non-base skins being white, as the old, non-base skins were a couple different colors.

Regardless, I've seen the in-game models thus far, and sorta hope that they update the splashes of Tango and Safecracker. The splashes should reflect the in-game models, unless they want to change the models' skin colors to match the splashes instead for whatever reason...?

{{sticker:sg-lux-2}}
